{"tid":1229221,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"今日遊行 命題一致 撤回惡法 林鄭下台","createTime":"2019-06-16T00:29:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T00:59:14.000Z","uid":82444,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b3092523c153649e7a9bca116f75c00bcda8dfea","tid":1229221,"uid":82444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T00:29:07.000Z","msg":"每個人心中都有自己意見<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但點解上星期有一百萬人出黎行 <br />\n就你因為今次遊行既目標好清</span></span>晰 <br />\n<br />\n大家無論係黃絲藍絲中立 都會受到呢條法例影響<br />\n<br />\n請大家記住 今次遊行目的 <br />\n唔係咩香港獨立 臨時政府 推翻中共 <br />\n唔好比人騎劫左個遊行 <br />\n<br />\n遊行目標清晰 一單還又一單 <br />\n命題單刀直入 唔比人有機會抽水扭曲遊行<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日 反送中 抗惡法 撤回逃犯修訂條例 林鄭下台</span></span>"},{"pid":"57d50a7bcb6728faadcde30bb8f7de0dd67da3ec","tid":1229221,"uid":82444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T00:33:44.000Z","msg":"人手置頂 <br />\n請大家唔好錯左重點 <br />\n兒登太多混淆視聽 打飛機Post <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭下台 撤回惡法</span></span>"},{"pid":"1ec95b61ce25d123f166c040700ed1ebe5dd84fa","tid":1229221,"uid":2156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T00:36:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>黑警冷血，林鄭殺港<br />\n無線新聞，出賣港人</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"2fa89e05e66e13084a0eabcd0eff62f6819e7c67","tid":1229221,"uid":82444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T00:42:23.000Z","msg":"人手置頂 <br />\n不要騎劫遊行<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭下台 撤回惡法</span></span>"},{"pid":"4a2911440a751e7be642df93bae2705edb005849","tid":1229221,"uid":6063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T00:59:14.000Z","msg":"痴線，最重要係救回被補義士啊"}]}